Cardiac risk in patients undergoing carotid endarterectomy: impact on 
perioperative and long-term mortality.

Mackey WC(1), O'Donnell TF Jr, Callow AD.

Author information:
(1)New England Medical Center, Tufts University Department of Surgery, Boston, 
